Ran, stop right there!
- Yeah, right!

00:00:20.854 --> 00:00:22.856 position:50% align:center
Like I'd ever stop!
- [gasps]

00:00:22.939 --> 00:00:25.191 position:50% align:center
- Kunai, I'm sorry
to make you wait!

00:00:25.734 --> 00:00:28.153 position:50% align:center
Time for a jail break.
[grunting]

00:00:28.236 --> 00:00:30.572 position:50% align:center
- Ran, you did that,
didn't you?

00:00:30.655 --> 00:00:32.073 position:50% align:center
- What'd you do this time?

00:00:32.157 --> 00:00:33.616 position:50% align:center
- [snickers]

00:00:33.700 --> 00:00:35.326 position:50% align:center
[all gasping]
You know.

00:00:35.410 --> 00:00:37.537 position:50% align:center
