the classroom ceiling.

00:00:37.620 --> 00:00:38.872 position:50% align:center
Boom!

00:00:39.956 --> 00:00:42.834 position:50% align:center
- Sheesh, again?
- [laughing]

00:00:43.335 --> 00:00:44.961 position:50% align:center
[groans]
There we go.

00:00:45.045 --> 00:00:47.547 position:50% align:center
[inhales and exhales sharply]

00:00:47.630 --> 00:00:49.507 position:50% align:center
I love the view
from up here.

00:00:49.591 --> 00:00:51.801 position:50% align:center
- How's school?
- Boring.

00:00:51.885 --> 00:00:53.511 position:50% align:center
I like how they feed me, though.

00:00:53.595 --> 00:00:55.764 position:50% align:center
- Come back
to the Pylon Apartment.

00:00:55.847 --> 00:00:58.558 position:50% align:center
Didn't your jerk
of a dad get arrested?

00:00:58.641 --> 00:01:00.226 position:50% align:center
- Yeah.
Serves him right.

00:01:01.644 --> 00:01:02.812 position:50% align:center
[exhales]

00:01:02.896 --> 00:01:04.397 position:50% align:center
But that does sound pretty good.

00:01:07.525 --> 00:01:09.903 position:50% align:center
Whoa, that's so cool!

00:01:09.986 --> 00:01:11.780 position:50% align:center
Isn't that Zeroth's graffiti?

00:01:11.863 --> 00:01:13.531 position:50% align:center
- That street artist
who's originally

00:01:13.615 --> 00:01:14.991 position:50% align:center
from the 24th ward?

00:01:15.658 --> 00:01:17.327 position:50% align:center
I heard he's back
in town right now.

00:01:17.410 --> 00:01:19.454 position:50% align:center
- Really?
That's so sick!

00:01:19.537 --> 00:01:21.956 position:50% align:center
Awesome!
What's it say?

00:01:22.040 --> 00:01:25.335 position:50% align:center
- It says that creation
is always an act of destruction

00:01:25.418 --> 00:01:27.462 position:50% align:center
in the beginning.
Hello, there.

00:01:27.545 --> 00:01:28.880 position:50% align:center
You like my graffiti?

