00:18:56.845 --> 00:18:58.304 position:50% align:center
into an art form.

00:18:58.388 --> 00:19:00.682 position:50% align:center
Because they were drawn
by Zeroth,

00:19:00.765 --> 00:19:02.267 position:50% align:center
scribbles that
would've been erased

00:19:02.350 --> 00:19:04.019 position:50% align:center
have been preserved
to this day.

00:19:04.811 --> 00:19:06.521 position:50% align:center
- This is the train car
where you detonated

00:19:06.604 --> 00:19:08.106 position:50% align:center
your first hacking bomb.

00:19:08.189 --> 00:19:11.401 position:50% align:center
- You mean this piece
of child's play?

00:19:11.484 --> 00:19:13.570 position:50% align:center
[buzzing and hissing]

00:19:13.653 --> 00:19:17.157 position:50% align:center
Even if I had skills,
if I can't use them properly,

00:19:17.240 --> 00:19:18.908 position:50% align:center
then I'm nothing more than
a criminal!

00:19:18.992 --> 00:19:20.452 position:50% align:center
- That's not true!

00:19:20.535 --> 00:19:23.038 position:50% align:center
You're not a criminal, Kunai!
You're a victim!

00:19:23.121 --> 00:19:25.874 position:50% align:center
- Repeating this stuff over
and over again,

00:19:25.957 --> 00:19:28.084 position:50% align:center
it's got no chance
of impressing anybody!

00:19:28.168 --> 00:19:30.879 position:50% align:center
- That's not true at all, Kunai!
You've always impressed me!

00:19:30.962 --> 00:19:33.214 position:50% align:center
That's why I kept going
as DoRed together with you!

00:19:33.298 --> 00:19:35.759 position:50% align:center
- Shut up!
Enough of the lip service!

00:19:35.842 --> 00:19:38.136 position:50% align:center
[indistinct chatter]
[slow swing music playing]

00:19:38.219 --> 00:19:40.388 position:50% align:center
- I don't have any time left.
Dammit!

00:19:40.472 --> 00:19:42.474 position:50% align:center
He's just never alone!

00:19:42.557 --> 00:19:44.392 position:50% align:center
Guess I gotta go for it!

00:19:44.476 --> 00:19:46.186 position:50% align:center
[grunts]
- [chuckling]

00:19:46.269 --> 00:19:48.646 position:50% align:center
[both grunting]

00:19:48.730 --> 00:19:49.731 position:50% align:center
- [grunts]
[gun cocking]

00:19:49.814 --> 00:19:51.232 position:50% align:center
[gunshot]
[both grunting]

00:19:51.316 --> 00:19:52.442 position:50% align:center
[all screaming]

00:19:52.525 --> 00:19:54.527 position:50% align:center
[all grunting]

00:19:56.529 --> 00:19:57.572 position:50% align:center
- [gasping]

00:19:57.655 --> 00:19:58.948 position:50% align:center
- What is going on?

00:19:59.032 --> 00:20:01.242 position:50% align:center
- I'm sorry
to cause such a riot.

00:20:01.326 --> 00:20:03.828 position:50% align:center
It would seem a burglar
who wants this hard drive

00:20:03.912 --> 00:20:05.205 position:50% align:center
has infiltrated the vessel.

00:20:05.288 --> 00:20:06.331 position:50% align:center
- How dare he?

00:20:06.414 --> 00:20:08.083 position:50% align:center
Catch him at any cost!

00:20:08.166 --> 00:20:10.335 position:50% align:center
- Shuta, disengage.
- Huh?

00:20:10.418 --> 00:20:12.003 position:50% align:center
- You need to get out
of there somehow.

00:20:12.087 --> 00:20:13.421 position:50% align:center
- Wait! What do you mean?
- I won't be able to help you

00:20:13.505 --> 00:20:14.673 position:50% align:center
- Wait! What do you mean?
- if you get caught.

00:20:14.756 --> 00:20:16.675 position:50% align:center
- Don't let him get away!
[guns cocking]

00:20:16.758 --> 00:20:17.967 position:50% align:center
[gunshots]
- Dammit!

00:20:18.051 --> 00:20:20.428 position:50% align:center
What the hell is up with Koki?

00:20:20.512 --> 00:20:22.931 position:50% align:center
- You're fully aware
of it all, too.

00:20:23.014 --> 00:20:24.891 position:50% align:center
The wealthy people aboard
that cruise ship

00:20:24.974 --> 00:20:26.601 position:50% align:center
are all good for nothing!

00:20:27.435 --> 00:20:29.396 position:50% align:center
No matter how many
innocent people die 'cause

00:20:29.479 --> 00:20:31.022 position:50% align:center
of Drug D,
they won't care as long

00:20:31.106 --> 00:20:33.400 position:50% align:center
as their own selfish desires
are fulfilled!

00:20:33.483 --> 00:20:35.360 position:50% align:center
So what's wrong with blowing
them all up starting

00:20:35.443 --> 00:20:36.945 position:50% align:center
with Howard Win?

00:20:37.028 --> 00:20:39.447 position:50% align:center
- Massacring people isn't how
we do things, is it?

00:20:39.531 --> 00:20:42.075 position:50% align:center
- [shudders]

00:20:42.158 --> 00:20:45.286 position:50% align:center
I'm certain that your art
will someday be able

00:20:45.370 --> 00:20:47.831 position:50% align:center
to change the hearts
of people across the world.

00:20:48.540 --> 00:20:50.834 position:50% align:center
But right now
there isn't enough time.

00:20:50.917 --> 00:20:53.003 position:50% align:center
You see it clearly
when you use D.

00:20:53.086 --> 00:20:54.713 position:50% align:center
It's dangerous.

00:20:54.796 --> 00:20:56.840 position:50% align:center
It kills reason.

00:20:56.923 --> 00:20:58.925 position:50% align:center
Anger and ecstasy
start welling up

00:20:59.009 --> 00:21:01.886 position:50% align:center
from deep inside you,
but because of that feeling

00:21:01.970 --> 00:21:03.638 position:50% align:center
I figured out what I needed
to do!

00:21:04.097 --> 00:21:05.807 position:50% align:center
Before it's too late,

00:21:05.890 --> 00:21:07.976 position:50% align:center
I will do something that I
can't do as an artist,

00:21:08.059 --> 00:21:09.436 position:50% align:center
but as a criminal!

00:21:09.519 --> 00:21:11.187 position:50% align:center
- That's crazy talk!
You are an artist!

00:21:11.271 --> 00:21:12.564 position:50% align:center
- This...
- [grunting]

00:21:12.647 --> 00:21:15.108 position:50% align:center
- Is how I do things now!

00:21:15.191 --> 00:21:16.484 position:50% align:center
- Shoot.
[gunshot]

00:21:16.568 --> 00:21:18.570 position:50% align:center
[glass shatters]

00:21:23.658 --> 00:21:25.326 position:50% align:center
- Kunai!
[gasps]

00:21:25.410 --> 00:21:28.246 position:50% align:center
[whimpering]

00:21:28.830 --> 00:21:30.165 position:50% align:center
- [gasps]

00:21:34.502 --> 00:21:36.087 position:50% align:center
- Kunai.

00:21:36.171 --> 00:21:38.506 position:50% align:center
- There's no room for choice
in this scenario.

00:21:38.590 --> 00:21:40.508 position:50% align:center
- Wha--Ko?

00:21:40.592 --> 00:21:42.635 position:50% align:center
- No matter who that guy is,

00:21:42.719 --> 00:21:44.679 position:50% align:center
I can't give any leeway
to criminals.

00:21:44.763 --> 00:21:46.139 position:50% align:center
[beeps]
- Criminals?

00:21:47.640 --> 00:21:49.809 position:50% align:center
Who's the real criminal
in this situation?

00:21:50.769 --> 00:21:53.438 position:50% align:center
Kunai's feelings,
his hesitation,

00:21:53.521 --> 00:21:55.523 position:50% align:center
his agony,
his life,

00:21:55.607 --> 00:21:57.650 position:50% align:center
none of them have value?
Is that what you're saying?

00:21:57.734 --> 00:21:58.735 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:21:58.818 --> 00:22:00.570 position:50% align:center
- There's no room for debate.

00:22:00.653 --> 00:22:02.155 position:50% align:center
Don't resist.

00:22:02.238 --> 00:22:05.617 position:50% align:center
- [shuddering]

00:22:08.453 --> 00:22:09.829 position:50% align:center
- Don't do it.
- [gasps]

00:22:11.039 --> 00:22:15.585 position:50% align:center
- You are an artist, Ran.

00:22:16.544 --> 00:22:18.088 position:50% align:center
- Kunai.

00:22:18.171 --> 00:22:19.297 position:50% align:center
- Hans up!

00:22:19.756 --> 00:22:23.134 position:50% align:center
- [shuddering]

00:22:29.224 --> 00:22:31.810 position:50% align:center
- So the incident ended
with the suspect shot dead, huh?

00:22:33.228 --> 00:22:34.896 position:50% align:center
It seems like the right answer,

00:22:34.979 --> 00:22:36.606 position:50% align:center
but then why don't
I feel relieved?

00:22:36.690 --> 00:22:38.024 position:50% align:center
[inhales and exhales sharply]

00:22:38.108 --> 00:22:39.859 position:50% align:center
And I can't contact either
of them.

00:22:39.943 --> 00:22:41.444 position:50% align:center
What's going on?

00:22:41.528 --> 00:22:43.655 position:50% align:center
Oh, man.
Muscle cramps really suck.

00:22:43.738 --> 00:22:44.823 position:50% align:center
- Hey, Shu!
- Oh, Kozue.

00:22:44.906 --> 00:22:47.117 position:50% align:center
- Get a look at this.
- Hmm?

00:22:47.200 --> 00:22:49.994 position:50% align:center
"My Father's Memory Illustrated
by DoRed."

00:22:50.078 --> 00:22:52.706 position:50% align:center
- So what do you think?
- You wrote it?

00:22:52.789 --> 00:22:55.166 position:50% align:center
- Yeah, because
of what you said.

00:22:55.250 --> 00:22:56.876 position:50% align:center
How it's not meaningless.

00:22:56.960 --> 00:22:58.920 position:50% align:center
I thought I should properly
write about my dad.

00:23:00.213 --> 00:23:02.257 position:50% align:center
I met a kind person
the other day

00:23:02.340 --> 00:23:05.051 position:50% align:center
who taught me that art
can actually change the world.

00:23:05.135 --> 00:23:08.179 position:50% align:center
Maybe the state of things really
will be different.

00:23:08.263 --> 00:23:10.682 position:50% align:center
- Yeah.
You're right.

00:23:10.765 --> 00:23:13.852 position:50% align:center
- [singing in Japanese]

00:23:13.935 --> 00:23:16.646 position:50% align:center
[Junya Enoki, Yuma Uchida,
and Kaito Ishikawa's

00:23:16.730 --> 00:23:18.231 position:50% align:center
"255,255,255"]

00:23:18.314 --> 00:23:21.151 position:50% align:center
[all singing in Japanese]

00:23:21.234 --> 00:23:28.158 position:50% align:center
♪ ♪

00:23:45.800 --> 00:23:48.136 position:50% align:center
- Koki helped prevent
a terrorist attack?

00:23:48.219 --> 00:23:50.347 position:50% align:center
The report,
thank you.

00:23:50.430 --> 00:23:53.683 position:50% align:center
Hmm, I suppose that the time
has finally come.

00:23:53.767 --> 00:23:55.268 position:50% align:center
[tense music]

00:23:55.352 --> 00:23:57.979 position:50% align:center
[beeping]

00:23:58.063 --> 00:23:59.397 position:50% align:center
- Yes.
- It's me.

00:23:59.481 --> 00:24:01.024 position:50% align:center
Are preparations complete?

00:24:01.107 --> 00:24:02.400 position:50% align:center
- Without issue.

00:24:02.484 --> 00:24:04.194 position:50% align:center
So, you'll be starting it, then?

00:24:04.277 --> 00:24:05.695 position:50% align:center
- Yes.

00:24:05.779 --> 00:24:07.947 position:50% align:center
By putting the KANAE System
into operation,

00:24:08.031 --> 00:24:11.034 position:50% align:center
I'll create a revolution
in the 24th ward.